v1.3.0
- Added: `filePathKeys` configuration for custom file navigation keywords (e.g., 'systemTestTemplate')
- Added: Task documentation caching to prevent duplicate HTTP requests
- Added: Hover request throttling to prevent multiple simultaneous fetches
- Added: Status bar feedback during task documentation fetching (with 5s timeout)
- Improved: Webpack bundle optimization (output file: extension-bundle.js, 49 KB)
- Improved: Performance optimizations (debounced decorations, large file skipping)
- Fixed: Task URLs now only open on Ctrl+click, not Ctrl+hover
- Fixed: Memory leaks in decoration timeout and cache cleanup
- Fixed: Null reference checks and error handling throughout
- Note: axios/cheerio are now optional dependencies (will auto-disable InternetFetch if missing)

v1.2.4
- Fixed: Task documentation URL navigation for certain tasks

v1.2.3
- Fixed: Template loading from different workspace folders

v1.2.2
- Fixed: Sonar lint errors and code refactoring

v1.2.1
- Updated: README and build configuration

v1.2.0
- Updated: npm packages and build configuration

v1.1.1
- Fixed: Multi-folder workspace navigation

v1.1.0
